Company Profile:MatchMove Global Pte Ltd (www.matchmove.com) is a Singapore-based digital entertainment and social enterprise solution provider that helps online businesses increase revenue, user engagement and loyalty through the strategic use of gamification, social networking and mobile commerce platforms. We have worked with some of the biggest names in the region such as Yahoo, Starhub, Resorts World Genting, TV3, Kompas, Okezone, Voice of Vietnam and more.We ranked 25th out of the 500 fastest-growing technology companies in the 2013 Deloitte Technology Fast 500 Asia Pacific ranking.With offices in Singapore, Vietnam, Indonesia, MatchMove’s reach in SE Asia is strongly established and the company looks to expand to other parts of Asia, the United States, India and the Middle East.
Job Description:To solicit and acquire new customers for the MatchMove wallet (www.mmvpay.com)Achieve targets for number of successful sign-upsInteract face to face or calls with local and foreign customersBe well versed with product knowledgeRequirements:Highly driven to excel in a sales-focused and fast-paced environmentStrong passion for sales and achieving sales targetExcellent interpersonal and communication skills, adaptable and willing to learnProficient in English and at least a local language to communicate with local and foreign workers in SingaporeNo working experience required as training will be provided
